1. please create a first admin, use this api (create_frist_admin_employee) 
2. use login api and get _id (please pass vid params in all the api header)
2. create a company, use this api  (update_company)
    1.ref (company id) create automatically and its unique
3.create a employee, use this api  (update_employee)
    1.please use this roles:[admin,manager,employee];
    2.ref (employee id) create automatically and its unique
4.Manage the roles, use this api  (update_employee)
5.get company this api fetch company record
6.get employee this api fetch employee record
7.get_subordinate thi api fetch all manager and subordinate users